{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Alliance de Salomon avec Hiram, roi de Tyr. \u2014 Pr\u00e9paratifs pour la construction du temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. 2 Ch 2. Esd 3:7. Ag 1:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Hiram, roi de Tyr, envoya ses serviteurs vers Salomon, car il apprit qu\u2019on l\u2019avait oint pour roi \u00e0 la place de son p\u00e8re, et il avait toujours aim\u00e9 David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2","name":"1 Rois 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.4.34","name":"1 Rois 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Salomon fit dire \u00e0 Hiram:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3","name":"1 Rois 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.1","name":"1 Rois 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tu sais que David, mon p\u00e8re, n\u2019a pas pu b\u00e2tir une maison \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, \u00e0 cause des guerres dont ses ennemis l\u2019ont envelopp\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel les e\u00fbt mis sous la plante de ses pieds.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4","name":"1 Rois 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2","name":"1 Rois 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Maintenant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, m\u2019a donn\u00e9 du repos de toutes parts; plus d\u2019adversaires, plus de calamit\u00e9s!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5","name":"1 Rois 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3","name":"1 Rois 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Voici, j\u2019ai l\u2019intention de b\u00e2tir une maison au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, comme l\u2019\u00c9ternel l\u2019a d\u00e9clar\u00e9 \u00e0 David, mon p\u00e8re, en disant: Ton fils que je mettrai \u00e0 ta place sur ton tr\u00f4ne, ce sera lui qui b\u00e2tira une maison \u00e0 mon nom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6","name":"1 Rois 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4","name":"1 Rois 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ordonne maintenant que l\u2019on coupe pour moi des c\u00e8dres du Liban. Mes serviteurs seront avec les tiens, et je te paierai le salaire de tes serviteurs tel que tu l\u2019auras fix\u00e9; car tu sais qu\u2019il n\u2019y a personne parmi nous qui s\u2019entende \u00e0 couper les bois comme les Sidoniens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7","name":"1 Rois 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5","name":"1 Rois 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il entendit les paroles de Salomon, Hiram eut une grande joie, et il dit: B\u00e9ni soit aujourd\u2019hui l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui a donn\u00e9 \u00e0 David un fils sage pour chef de ce grand peuple!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8","name":"1 Rois 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6","name":"1 Rois 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et Hiram fit r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 Salomon: J\u2019ai entendu ce que tu m\u2019as envoy\u00e9 dire. Je ferai tout ce qui te plaira au sujet des bois de c\u00e8dre et des bois de cypr\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9","name":"1 Rois 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7","name":"1 Rois 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mes serviteurs les descendront du Liban \u00e0 la mer, et je les exp\u00e9dierai par mer en radeaux jusqu\u2019au lieu que tu m\u2019indiqueras; l\u00e0, je les ferai d\u00e9lier, et tu les prendras. Ce que je d\u00e9sire en retour, c\u2019est que tu fournisses des vivres \u00e0 ma maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10","name":"1 Rois 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8","name":"1 Rois 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Hiram donna \u00e0 Salomon des bois de c\u00e8dre et des bois de cypr\u00e8s autant qu\u2019il en voulut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11","name":"1 Rois 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9","name":"1 Rois 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et Salomon donna \u00e0 Hiram vingt mille cors de froment pour l\u2019entretien de sa maison et vingt cors d\u2019huile d\u2019olives concass\u00e9es; c\u2019est ce que Salomon donna chaque ann\u00e9e \u00e0 Hiram.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12","name":"1 Rois 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10","name":"1 Rois 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel donna de la sagesse \u00e0 Salomon, comme il le lui avait promis. Et il y eut paix entre Hiram et Salomon, et ils firent alliance ensemble.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13","name":"1 Rois 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11","name":"1 Rois 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le roi Salomon leva sur tout Isra\u00ebl des hommes de corv\u00e9e; ils \u00e9taient au nombre de trente mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14","name":"1 Rois 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12","name":"1 Rois 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il les envoya au Liban, dix mille par mois alternativement; ils \u00e9taient un mois au Liban, et deux mois chez eux. Adoniram \u00e9tait pr\u00e9pos\u00e9 sur les hommes de corv\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15","name":"1 Rois 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13","name":"1 Rois 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Salomon avait encore soixante-dix mille hommes qui portaient les fardeaux et quatre-vingt mille qui taillaient les pierres dans la montagne,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16","name":"1 Rois 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14","name":"1 Rois 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>sans compter les chefs, au nombre de trois mille trois cents, pr\u00e9pos\u00e9s par Salomon sur les travaux et charg\u00e9s de surveiller les ouvriers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17","name":"1 Rois 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15","name":"1 Rois 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Le roi ordonna d\u2019extraire de grandes et magnifiques pierres de taille pour les fondements de la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18","name":"1 Rois 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16","name":"1 Rois 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 5:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Les ouvriers de Salomon, ceux de Hiram, et les Guibliens, les taill\u00e8rent, et ils pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent les bois et les pierres pour b\u00e2tir la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5","name":"1 Rois 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1","name":"1 Rois 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17","name":"1 Rois 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb2819f28.64361792');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2819f28.64361792\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb2819f28.64361792","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb2819f28.64361792'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2819f28.64361792\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}